longBusinessSummary: Lee & Man Chemical Company Limited, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells chemical products in the People's Republic of China. It operates through two segments, Chemical and Property. The company offers caustic soda, chloromethane products, polymers, hydrogen peroxide, fluorochemical products, polytetrafluoroethylene, liquified chlorine, and other products, as well as provides styrene acrylic latex surface sizing agent and lithium-ion battery additives. In addition, it is involved in the development, sale, and rental of properties. Lee & Man Chemical Company Limited was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Kwun Tong, Hong Kong.
